              <En>A facility where buses are parked, maintained, and dispatched during shifts.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="c20af3e1-fec8-4495-8a08-2f56964d6978">
              <Vi>Kho chứa vũ khí và vật tư quân sự trong căn cứ.</Vi>
              <En>A secure facility for storing weapons, ammunition, and military supplies.</En>
